Applicable to children under the age of eight.
Features:
- Complete a lovely look with this mini school bag for your kid.
- Made of SBR material, good durability and lightweight.
- Breathable and soft shoulder straps, slow down stress for children.
- Enough space for children to carry books and some travel's goods.

There is plenty of room for holding the thermos, sandwich and small toys. If you took a bottle of water, yogurt or juice, you'd be able to fit a bit more.

Product Name（产品标题）: XF808 Wireless Digital Video Baby Monitor Night Vision Temperature Sensor
Description (Non-HTML Format)（产品描述非HTML格:
Description:
As we all know that taking care of the newborn can be one of the most special and rewarding experiences of your life, you may think how can you give your child constant attention and care.
Our wireless baby monitor just likes a loving friend, not only shows you every moment of your little angle but also keeps safe and private communication with your baby.
In other words, they can play and explore, you can watch them play and explore.
Features:
High-resolution color LCD monitor
3.5 inch LCD colored display screen with the 2.4GHz wireless audio video receiver
Unobstructed effective range
Up to 100m transmission range in open space, having more freedom in nursing baby
Music player
Built-in lullabies, which may help the parent comfort the baby fall into sleep
2-way audio communication
Comfort your baby by using the two-way talkback intercom function
Temperature detection
With temperature sensor, supervise baby's room temperature all the day, care your baby's health
2 working modes (Normal/VOX)
VOX mode is the power-saving mode with voice activation, you could focus on your things until the monitor is activated
Infrared night vision
Allows you to pick up clear images in the dark, keeping an eye on baby all night
Long battery life
3.7V 700mAh Li-ion battery (included), provides longer working time
Other functions
Adjustable volume and LCD brightness controls, switchable temperature unit
Specifications:
Monitor:
LCD size: 3.5 inch
Resolution supported: 960 x 240
Receiving sensitivity: -88dBm
Power supply: DC 5V
Battery: built-in 3.7V Li-ion battery
Camera:
Image sensor: 1/3 inch COMS
Night vision distance: 15 FT (5m)
Power supply: DC 5V
View angle: 70 degree
Methods:
Connect the main socket to get start the baby/parent unit, a green light will display indicate the baby unit is working
Fully charge the parent unit before using, press and hold the power key to turn on it
Place the baby unit in a suitable place and adjust the viewing angle of the camera until you are satisfied with the image in the parent unit
Power Consumption: DC 5V
Powered Source: Rechargeable Battery
Feature: Intercom,LCD Display,Music,Nightlight
Pattern Type: Others
LCD Size: 3.5 inch
Batteries Required: Yes
Technical Feature: Infrared
0.456 Package weight: 0.505 kg
Package size (L x W x H): 18.40 x 14.80 x 7.00 cm / 7.24 x 5.83 x 2.76 inches
Package Content: 1 x Monitor, 1 x Camera, 2 x Power Adapter, 1 x English Instruction

Product Name（产品标题）: LETING 6-in-1 Baby Nail File for Toes and Fingernails Electric Manicure Set
Description (Non-HTML Format)（产品描述非HTML格:
Brief Description:
Feel distressed when your baby scratches his/her innocent face? Want to trim your newborn baby's nails while worrying about hurting your little one?
LETING Electric Baby Nail File Set will be a great solution. With the 6-in-1 design, multiple types of gritting sandpapers for your option, safe to trim nails. Suitable for newborns, toddlers or adults!
Main Features:
- Safe Baby Nail Care Tool
You can safely and quickly trim and polish babies' little toenails and fingernails, buffing and shaping, won't damage cuticles or soft nail beds.
- 6-in-1 Design
Equipped with 6 cushioned sandpapers in precise grit levels, meet the needs of trimming nails for newborns and adults.
- Multiple Speeds Control
Two speeds (high/low) and two rotations (clockwise/reverse) for choices, enhancing trimming smoother nails.
- Quiet Operation
You can trim your babies' nails while they're sleeping without disturbing them.
- With LED Light
Come with a front LED light, effectively ensuring safe when using it in the dark night.
- Ergonomic Handle
Pretty curve design gives a painless, smooth and comfortable grip feeling during nail-care operation.
- Portable Design
With a storage case, easy to carry, can be used in the professional studio, home and travel.
5 Working Modes:
R2 - rotating in counterclockwise with high speed
R1 - rotating in counterclockwise with low speed
0 - off mode
L1 - rotating in clockwise with low speed
L2 - rotating in clockwise with high speed
Specifications:
Materials: ABS
Power supply: 2 x AA battery (not included)
Voltage: 3V 0.87W 290mA (max.)
Type: Other Accessories
Material: ABS
0.228 Package weight: 0.264 kg
Package size (L x W x H): 9.00 x 5.50 x 16.00 cm / 3.54 x 2.17 x 6.3 inches
Package Contents: 1 x Main Unit, 3 x Filing Tool for Adult, 3 x Cushioned Grinding Head for Baby, 1 x Storage Case, 1 x English User Manual
